**Pack Warlock** | Werewolf Transformation
__Basics__
Every other night, the Pack Warlock may check another player's role
__Details__
Every other night, the Pack Warlock may inspect a player. They will be told what that player's role is. 
Inspecting a player is an immediate ability. The Pack Warlock is affected by weak disguises, redirections, and obstructions.
The Pack Warlock is not a lycan, but is part of the wolfpack

